&lt;p&gt;The BCG vaccination service is looking for an experienced administrator, preferably with previous experience of working in a busy office environment, to be part of a dynamic team in delivering an effective service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be supporting the manager and team members within the service providing an effective and timely administrative support to the day to day work for the team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder must be able to project a positive and professional manner to both team members and other healthcare professionals that you will come in contact with and be able to manage a variety of different tasks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Must be confident in Microsoft and database systems and able to communicate effectively with a range of people by phone and ensure that all calls are dealt with effectively and appropriately&lt;/p&gt;
